title: HAWAII UPDATE: GO KART SESH
description: Evan, Conner and Miggy escape the North Shore flat spell by heading to the race track. Evan talks up a lot of game, but in the end blames his faulty go kart and can't finish in front of a speedy Conner Coffin. Stay tuned for more updates, as there looks to finally be a bit of swell on the horizon. Video: PK
